text:
This is a hidden gem, and I really wanted to gate-keep, but decided that we should share good hawker food so that the business can stay afloat and we can all continue to enjoy the good and affordable food.

I've tried the pig's trotter, dry BKT and herbal chicken. All are good. Absolute favourite is pig's trotter. Eat liao will  GDLL ðŸ¥²
